{"data":[{"name":"80:1","price":"眉をひそめて、背を向けた、","arabic":"عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5759,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿabasa watawallā ","translations":["He frowned","and turned away","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿabasa","watawallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,790],[2,790,2185]]}},{"name":"80:2","price":"自分のもとに、盲目の者が来たために。¹","arabic":"أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلۡأَعۡمَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5760,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　アッ＝ラーズィー* によれば、解釈学者らは、このアーヤ*が預言者*ムハンマド*と教友*イブン・ウンム・マクトゥームに関して下ったということで、一致している（１１：５３参照）。預言者*はある時、クライシュ族*の有力者らがムスリム*になることを望み、彼らをイスラーム*へと熱心に招いていた。そのような場にやって来た盲目のイブン・ウンム・マクトゥーム*の教えを彼にしつこくせがんでしまう。預言者*は話を邪魔されるのを嫌い、彼を相手にせず、有力者たちへの話に勤しんだ。このアーヤ*が下ってそのことを咎められた後、預言者*は彼を大事に扱い、重用するようになった（アル＝バガウィー５：２１０参照）。尚、預言者*・使徒*の無謬（むびゅう）性については、雌牛章３６の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"an jāahu al-aʿmā ","translations":["Because","came to him","the blind man","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["an","jāahu","al-aʿmā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,3530],[3,3530,4575]]}},{"name":"80:3","price":"そして、何があなたに（彼の真実を）知らせるのか？彼が清められる¹かもしれない、ということを？","arabic":"وَمَا يُدۡرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُۥ يَزَّكَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5761,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　ここでの「清められる」とは、預言者*からの教えを得ることで、自らの宗教においてより清浄となり、無知という闇が消えさること、とされる（アル＝クルトゥビー１９：２１３参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā yud'rīka laʿallahu yazzakkā ","translations":["But what","would make you know","that he might","purify himself","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","yud'rīka","laʿallahu","yazzakkā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,700],[2,700,1770],[3,1770,2980],[4,2980,4465]]}},{"name":"80:4","price":"あるいは、彼が教訓を受け、それで教訓が彼を益するかもしれないことを？","arabic":"أَوۡ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5762,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"aw yadhakkaru fatanfaʿahu al-dhik'rā ","translations":["Or","be reminded","so would benefit him","the reminder","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["aw","yadhakkaru","fatanfaʿahu","al-dhik'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,420],[2,420,1670],[3,1670,3590],[4,3590,5265]]}},{"name":"80:5","price":"（導きなしでも）十分だとする者¹はといえば、","arabic":"أَمَّا مَنِ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5763,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　これは善への意欲がないため、質問も教示も請うこともないようなもののこと（アッ＝サアディー９１０頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ammā mani is'taghnā ","translations":["As for","(him) who","considers himself free from need","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["ammā","mani","is'taghnā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1460],[2,1460,1850],[3,1850,2995]]}},{"name":"80:6","price":"あなたは彼に掛かりきり。","arabic":"فَأَنتَ لَهُۥ تَصَدَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5764,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-anta lahu taṣaddā ","translations":["So you","to him","give attention","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-anta","lahu","taṣaddā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1500],[2,1500,2070],[3,2070,3385]]}},{"name":"80:7","price":"彼が清められずとも、あなたには何のお咎めもないというのに。","arabic":"وَمَا عَلَيۡكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5765,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā ʿalayka allā yazzakkā ","translations":["And not","upon you","that not","he purifies himself","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","ʿalayka","allā","yazzakkā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1550],[3,1550,2450],[4,2450,3885]]}},{"name":"80:8","price":"そして（あなたと会うことに）意気込んで、あなたのもとにやって来た者はといえば、","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5766,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ammā man jāaka yasʿā ","translations":["But as for","(he) who","came to you","striving","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ammā","man","jāaka","yasʿā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1740],[2,1740,2860],[3,2860,5010],[4,5010,6085]]}},{"name":"80:9","price":"（アッラー*を）恐れているというのに、","arabic":"وَهُوَ يَخۡشَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5767,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wahuwa yakhshā ","translations":["While he","fears","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["wahuwa","yakhshā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,1635]]}},{"name":"80:10","price":"あなたは彼をそっちのけにしている。","arabic":"فَأَنتَ عَنۡهُ تَلَهَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5768,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-anta ʿanhu talahhā ","translations":["But you","from him","(are) distracted","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-anta","ʿanhu","talahhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1310],[2,1310,1940],[3,1940,3135]]}},{"name":"80:11","price":"断じて（、使徒*よ、あなたがしたようなことは、許され）ない！実にそれ（このスーラ*）は、教訓なのだ。","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذۡكِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5769,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā innahā tadhkiratun ","translations":["Nay","Indeed, it","(is) a reminder","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","innahā","tadhkiratun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2699],[2,2699,4269],[3,4269,5804]]}},{"name":"80:12","price":"そして誰でも（教訓を）望む者は、それ（啓示）を熟慮せよ。","arabic":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5770,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"faman shāa dhakarahu ","translations":["So whosoever","wills","may remember it","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["faman","shāa","dhakarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,940],[2,940,3370],[3,3370,4535]]}},{"name":"80:13","price":"（このクルアーン*は）貴い書巻¹の中、","arabic":"فِي صُحُفٖ مُّكَرَّمَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5771,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「貴い書巻」とは、守られし碑板*、あるいは啓典のこと（アル＝バガウィー５：２１０参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fī ṣuḥufin mukarramatin ","translations":["In","sheets","honored","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["fī","ṣuḥufin","mukarramatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,430],[2,430,1160],[3,1160,3425]]}},{"name":"80:14","price":"（位）高く、（あらゆる不純さや改変から）清浄な（書巻の中）、","arabic":"مَّرۡفُوعَةٖ مُّطَهَّرَةِۭ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5772,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"marfūʿatin muṭahharatin ","translations":["Exalted","purified","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["marfūʿatin","muṭahharatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,3795]]}},{"name":"80:15","price":"使いの者（天使*）たちの手許にある。","arabic":"بِأَيۡدِي سَفَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5773,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"bi-aydī safaratin ","translations":["In (the) hands","(of) scribes","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["bi-aydī","safaratin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1010],[2,1010,2125]]}},{"name":"80:16","price":"高貴で、善良な者たちの（手許に）。","arabic":"كِرَامِۭ بَرَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5774,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kirāmin bararatin ","translations":["Noble","dutiful","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["kirāmin","bararatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1520],[2,1520,2785]]}},{"name":"80:17","price":"（不信仰な）人間が、成敗されますよう。彼は（自分の主*に対し）、何とひどい不信仰に陥っていることか！","arabic":"قُتِلَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَآ أَكۡفَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5775,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"qutila al-insānu mā akfarahu ","translations":["Is destroyed","[the] man","how","ungrateful is he","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["qutila","al-insānu","mā","akfarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,2770],[3,2770,4540],[4,4540,5905]]}},{"name":"80:18","price":"かれ（アッラー*）は彼を、いかなるものからお創りになったのか？","arabic":"مِنۡ أَيِّ شَيۡءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5776,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"min ayyi shayin khalaqahu ","translations":["From","what","thing","He created him","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["min","ayyi","shayin","khalaqahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,460],[2,460,1070],[3,1070,1940],[4,1940,3225]]}},{"name":"80:19","price":"一滴の精液から彼をお創りになり、それを（徐々に）調整されたのだ。¹","arabic":"مِن نُّطۡفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ فَقَدَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5777,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「その各身体器官、美醜（びしゅう）、大小、不幸な者となるか、幸福なものとなるか、ということなどをお決めになった」という解釈もある（アル＝クルトゥビー１９：２１８参照）。尚、人間の創造の変遷（へんせん）については、巡礼*章５、信仰者たち章１４を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"min nuṭ'fatin khalaqahu faqaddarahu ","translations":["From","a semen-drop","He created him","then He proportioned him","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["min","nuṭ'fatin","khalaqahu","faqaddarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,340],[2,340,2500],[3,2500,3560],[4,3560,5325]]}},{"name":"80:20","price":"それからかれ（アッラー*）は、道を容易くされ、¹","arabic":"ثُمَّ ٱلسَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5778,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「道」には、「母親の胎内から出て来ること」「真理と虚偽の道、及びその判別（人間章３とその訳注も参照）」「各自が運命づけられた物事」といった解釈がある（アル＝バガウィー５：２１１参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma al-sabīla yassarahu ","translations":["Then","the way","He made easy for him","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","al-sabīla","yassarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,2530],[3,2530,4055]]}},{"name":"80:21","price":"やがては彼に死を与えられ、墓にお埋めになり、","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُۥ فَأَقۡبَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5779,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma amātahu fa-aqbarahu ","translations":["Then","He causes him to die","and provides a grave for him","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","amātahu","fa-aqbarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1240],[2,1240,2640],[3,2640,4435]]}},{"name":"80:22","price":"それから、かれがお望みになったら、（清算と報いのために、）彼を生き返させ給う。","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِذَا شَآءَ أَنشَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5780,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma idhā shāa ansharahu ","translations":["Then","when","He wills","He will resurrect him","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","idhā","shāa","ansharahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1470],[2,1470,2070],[3,2070,4340],[4,4340,6435]]}},{"name":"80:23","price":"断じて（、不信仰者*の状況は正しく）ない！彼は、かれ（アッラー*）が自分にご命じになったこと¹を、遂行してはないないのだから。","arabic":"كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقۡضِ مَآ أَمَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5781,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　つまり信仰と、かれへの服従ということ（ムヤッサル５８５頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā lammā yaqḍi mā amarahu ","translations":["Nay","Not","he has accomplished","what","He commanded him","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","lammā","yaqḍi","mā","amarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,920],[2,920,2410],[3,2410,3170],[4,3170,5100],[5,5100,6435]]}},{"name":"80:24","price":"ならば人間に、自分の食べ物（が、いかに創造されたか）について考えさせてみよ。","arabic":"فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِۦٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5782,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"falyanẓuri al-insānu ilā ṭaʿāmihi ","translations":["Then let look","the man","at","his food","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["falyanẓuri","al-insānu","ilā","ṭaʿāmihi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1990],[2,1990,3930],[3,3930,4510],[4,4510,6185]]}},{"name":"80:25","price":"われら*は、（地上に）水をざあざあと降らせ、","arabic":"أَنَّا صَبَبۡنَا ٱلۡمَآءَ صَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5783,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"annā ṣababnā al-māa ṣabban ","translations":["That [We]","[We] poured","the water","(in) abundance","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["annā","ṣababnā","al-māa","ṣabban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1620],[2,1620,2530],[3,2530,4850],[4,4850,5935]]}},{"name":"80:26","price":"それから大地を、ひび割れさせ（、そこから各種の植物を芽出せさせ）たのだ。","arabic":"ثُمَّ شَقَقۡنَا ٱلۡأَرۡضَ شَقّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5784,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma shaqaqnā al-arḍa shaqqan ","translations":["Then","We cleaved","the earth","splitting","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","shaqaqnā","al-arḍa","shaqqan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1630],[2,1630,2520],[3,2520,3410],[4,3410,4735]]}},{"name":"80:27","price":"そして、われら*はそこに種粒を生育させた、","arabic":"فَأَنۢبَتۡنَا فِيهَا حَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5785,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-anbatnā fīhā ḥabban ","translations":["Then We caused to grow","therein","grain","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-anbatnā","fīhā","ḥabban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2290],[2,2290,3190],[3,3190,4245]]}},{"name":"80:28","price":"また、葡萄、まぐさ、","arabic":"وَعِنَبٗا وَقَضۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5786,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waʿinaban waqaḍban ","translations":["And grapes","and green fodder","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["waʿinaban","waqaḍban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1420],[2,1420,3125]]}},{"name":"80:29","price":"オリーブ、ナツメヤシ、","arabic":"وَزَيۡتُونٗا وَنَخۡلٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5787,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wazaytūnan wanakhlan ","translations":["And olive","and date-palms","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["wazaytūnan","wanakhlan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1570],[2,1570,4155]]}},{"name":"80:30","price":"木深い農園、","arabic":"وَحَدَآئِقَ غُلۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5788,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waḥadāiqa ghul'ban ","translations":["And gardens","(of) thick foliage","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["waḥadāiqa","ghul'ban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2730],[2,2730,3665]]}},{"name":"80:31","price":"果実、牧草も（生育させた）、","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٗ وَأَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5789,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wafākihatan wa-abban ","translations":["And fruits","and grass","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["wafākihatan","wa-abban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1570],[2,1570,3345]]}},{"name":"80:32","price":"あなた方と、あなた方の家畜の利益のために。","arabic":"مَّتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5790,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"matāʿan lakum wali-anʿāmikum ","translations":["(As) a provision","for you","and for your cattle","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["matāʿan","lakum","wali-anʿāmikum",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,920],[2,920,1860],[3,1860,4165]]}},{"name":"80:33","price":"そして、（復活の日*を知らせる）轟きの一声¹が到来した時（、人々は自分の事で、掛かりきりになる）。","arabic":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلصَّآخَّةُ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5791,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「轟きの一声」は、一説に、角笛が吹き鳴らされること（アル＝バイダーウィー５：４５４参照）。家畜章７３とその訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-idhā jāati al-ṣākhatu ","translations":["But when","comes","the Deafening Blast","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-idhā","jāati","al-ṣākhatu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,670],[2,670,3299],[3,3299,7384]]}},{"name":"80:34","price":"人間が、（その恐怖ゆえに、）自分の兄弟から逃げ出す日、","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَفِرُّ ٱلۡمَرۡءُ مِنۡ أَخِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5792,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma yafirru al-maru min akhīhi ","translations":["(The) Day","will flee","a man","from","his brother","(34)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","yafirru","al-maru","min","akhīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,1570],[3,1570,2510],[4,2510,2800],[5,2800,5385]]}},{"name":"80:35","price":"また、自分の母親、父親、","arabic":"وَأُمِّهِۦ وَأَبِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5793,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ummihi 